1: "wget" or "git clone https://github.com/xianglei/phpHiveAdmin.git"

2:. untar it.

3: add this follow to your nginx.conf in your "location ~ .php$ {};" area

fastcgi_connect_timeout 36000; fastcgi_send_timeout 36000; fastcgi_read_timeout 36000;

4: in php 5.3.9 open $PHP_HOME/etc/php-fpm.conf modify to this:

process_control_timeout = 36000s

and to this:

request_terminate_timeout = 36000s

open $PHP_HOME/lib/php.ini modify to this:

max_input_time = 36000

and to this:

default_socket_timeout = 36000

5: restart nginx && php-fpm